<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>胖妖怪在洞里喊道：“我们已经吃了唐僧了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，你们最好离开！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！”八戒跪下，大哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净擦了擦流出的泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可怜的师父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空对着师弟们皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们俩居然相信那妖怪的话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他叹了口气。“在这里等着。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变成蛾子飞进了洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他就发现唐僧被绑在一个阴暗的房间里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变回原样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空！”唐僧大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘘。”悟空解开了唐僧，“小声点儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空念了个咒语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，外面传来了打呼噜的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的咒语让胖妖怪和小妖们睡着了。”悟空说，“快走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和唐僧从洞里出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和悟净高兴极了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父，我还以为你被吃了呢。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道他会没事的。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我要彻底消灭这些妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抽出金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金箍棒一直长到树那么大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“退后。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空挥起了金箍棒，砸坏了整个洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>岩石爆炸掉下来，堆到了一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看着石头堆，笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几周后，师徒四人来到一个小村子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒肚子里发出特别大的咕噜噜的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“我们该找吃的了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看见一个老和尚走过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好心的和尚。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您知道哪儿能要到食物吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们肚子很饿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老和尚点了点头。“你们去寇员外家吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“寇员外说要款待一万名佛教和尚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一定会给你们食物的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉了唐僧去寇员外家的路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人来到寇员外家门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人让他们进去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇员外的家又大又漂亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇员外出来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们好。”他微笑着说，“快请进。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人和寇员外一起坐在一个大房间里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个仆人端来了茶和点心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您款待我们，寇员外。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听说您要款待一万名和尚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”寇员外说，“我一辈子赚了很多钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我也想做善事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我希望有一天能重生为菩萨或佛祖。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，寇员外。”八戒说，“今天您运气很好！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我自己就能吃掉一万名和尚的食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，您如果给我吃的，就会成佛祖的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我今天的运气确实很好。”寇员外说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨晚我算了一下我款待过多少位和尚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>至今，我款待了9996名。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为了实现我的承诺，我再款待四位就行了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他脸上微笑着，“你们正好是四位！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，寇员外举办盛宴，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请来了村里所有的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人、寇员外和寇员外的夫人坐在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒看着摆在桌子上的好吃的东西，直流口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“面条、面包、蘑菇……不知道该先吃什么了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们吃的时候，寇员外靠近唐僧，说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要去哪儿啊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去西天。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去佛祖那里取真经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇员外眼睛一亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您是我的贵客呀！我不能让您走！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>